data.description: Cozy modern country inspired home with many updates sitting on over 1.5 acres.  Quick access to US 40 and a short drive to I-70.  Cozy up to a fire on a crisp day or walk through the wood during the fall.  Plenty of room for family and friends.  The main level features two living rooms, 2 bedrooms and a full bath.  Upstairs you'll find three more bedrooms and another full bath.  The large backyard is fully fenced with an area that would be perfect for a large vegetable garden.  You don't want to miss out on this amazing opportunity to enjoy the quiet country life!
